data.title: Good food and good specials
data.text: I fell into this place due to a rain storm.  The service was a bit slow but the food was good.  I ordered the daily special and it was very good for $799.  Included sandwich, soup and a drink.

data.title: Clean and Delicious Cafe
data.text:
We stopped in for a sandwich today and had a great experience. I love that the owner is right there on the premises making the food and was quite personable. 
The Roast Beef sandwich was loaded with veggies and cheese and it came with a can of soda and a bag of ships for $7.99. 
We also had an Italian Sub Sandwich that was also plentiful. 
I noticed the floors, tabletops and all food prep areas were sparkling clean.
It's walking distance to the courthouse so no reason to pop in and give it a try if you go for Jury Duty.
